    public abstract class AbstractStatefulReactor<I,S extends com.google.protobuf.Message,B extends io.spine.protobuf.ValidatingBuilder<S>>
extends AbstractEventReactor
    An abstract base for AbstractEventReactors which have state and require delivering the messages through an Inbox.
